title: Alexandra Daddario  / Acupuncture
description: Dr. Wali meets the business end of a bee and gives her clear view of blue light blocking glasses with Sean. Alexandra Daddario shares some sharp points about acupuncture and the unusual place she has had the needle. Listen to the episode to find out where!
